videos.description: Will Barton skies and splits two Suns' defenders for the lay-in.

videos.headline: Barton slices and dices for the layup

videos.description: Aaron Gordon grabs the steal and displays his handles on the way to a two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gordon dazzles on fast-break dunk) 2021/6/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gordon dazzles on fast-break dunk

videos.description: Chris Paul races in transition to toss the lob to Mikal Bridges for a huge flush.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mikal Bridges takes flight for alley-oop jam from CP3) 2021/6/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mikal Bridges takes flight for alley-oop jam from CP3

videos.description: Chris Paul toys with the Nuggets as he drains a smooth jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (CP3 goes in to his bag of tricks for mid-range jumper) 2021/6/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: CP3 goes in to his bag of tricks for mid-range jumper

videos.description: Nikola Jokic is ejected from the game after he commits a hard foul on Cameron Payne and has to be separated from Devin Booker.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Jokic ejected after hard foul on Payne, scrum with Booker) 2021/6/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jokic ejected after hard foul on Payne, scrum with Booker

videos.description: Chris Paul absorbs contact for the layup and gets up smiling as his teammates help him up.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (CP3 gets up smiling after tough and-1) 2021/6/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: CP3 gets up smiling after tough and-1

videos.description: Deandre Ayton rocks the rim with a two-handed jam as Suns sweep the Nuggets in the second round.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ayton puts the exclamation point on Suns' sweep) 2021/6/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ayton puts the exclamation point on Suns' sweep

videos.description: Devin Booker and Chris Paul enter the stands to hug their families as the Suns sweep the Nuggets to head to the Western Conference finals.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Booker, CP3 celebrate with family after Suns clinch spot in WCF) 2021/6/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Booker, CP3 celebrate with family after Suns clinch spot in WCF

videos.description: Chris Paul and Devin Booker combine for 71 points to help the Suns steamroll their way into the Western Conference finals for the first time in 11 years.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (CP3, Booker put up 71 to send Suns to sweep of Nuggets, 1st WCF since 2010) 2021/6/13 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: CP3, Booker put up 71 to send Suns to sweep of Nuggets, 1st WCF since 2010

videos.description: Nikola Jokic explains what he was trying to do when he was ejected for a hard foul on Cameron Payne as the Nuggets get swept by the Suns.

videos.headline: Jokic reacts to his ejection in Nuggets' loss
